  <TITLE>Combine some admin area pages into single ones</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>To simplify management. Here is a list of suggested pages: 1. Reports (all reports will be there) - new menu item 2. Customer &gt; Activity Log. Combine child pages to a single page with tabs 3. Content. News items + News comments 4. Content. Blog posts + Blog comments 5. Configuration &gt; Tax. Tax providers + Tax categories 6. Configuration &gt; Plugins. Local plugins + all plugins and themes 7. System &gt; Category templates, Manufacturer templates, Product templates + Topic templates 8. Catalog &gt; Bulk Edit. Just remove from menu, do not remove the page. Move to product list page as a &quot;Bulk Edit&quot; button (it will link to this page). Still discussing final list of pages... related to https://github.com/nopSolutions/nopCommerce/issues/1647</DESCRIPTION>
